unt has allowed me to do this. I try not to over engineer the build process.","position":{"start":{"line":99,"column":1,"offset":8188},"end":{"line":99,"column":239,"offset":8426}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":99,"column":1,"offset":8188},"end":{"line":99,"column":239,"offset":8426}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"raw","value":"<h3 id=\"human-am-i\">I am a Human</h3>","position":{"start":{"line":101,"column":1,"offset":8428},"end":{"line":101,"column":38,"offset":8465}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Finally I should say that at best I do this only about 60-70% of the time. Sometimes for small projects I very loosely apply these guidelines or don't follow them at all. Sometimes I'm lazy or tired or I'm tricked into thinking some marketing element will only be on the homepage for \"2 weeks absolute maximum\" and it's Friday so I just do it quickly. Two years later it's still there. I'm ok with that, these are only guidelines and we are humans not machines.","position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1,"offset":8467},"end":{"line":103,"column":462,"offset":8928}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":103,"column":1,"offset":8467},"end":{"line":103,"column":462,"offset":8928}}},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"strong","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Final disclaimer","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":3,"offset":8932},"end":{"line":105,"column":19,"offset":8948}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1,"offset":8930},"end":{"line":105,"column":21,"offset":8950}}},{"type":"text","value":": Things are constantly changing. This might not be how I CSS in the future. And ok, I guess this is kind of an 'in response' article.","position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":21,"offset":8950},"end":{"line":105,"column":155,"offset":9084}}}],"position":{"start":{"line":105,"column":1,"offse